name: Fauna Flowers 08 - Tatu Flower
description:
A tiny timid little armored flower. It is almost impossible to harm this one. Whenever it feels threatened, it closes to protect itself. It gets strong and impenetrable, like a natural armor. Its roots penetrate the soil and travel trough tunnels forming a majestic underground maze.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
